==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unroofed
<hw>Un*roofed"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<ety>[Properly p. p. of <ets>unroof</ets>.]</ety> <def>Stripped of a
roof, or similar covering.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Broken carriages, dead horses, <qex>unroofed</qex> cottages, all
indicated the movements.</q> <rj><qau>Sir W. Scott.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <ety>[Pref. <ets>un-</ets> not +
<ets>roofed</ets>.]</ety> <def>Not yet roofed.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unroost</ent>⟦br⟧
